      <title>银行称存款上升后 NYCB 股价转正</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/nycb-stock-turns-positive-after-bank-says-deposits-have-climbed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约社区银行 (New York Community Bancorp) 扭转了早前的亏损，该公司股价周二触及 27 年来的最低点，该公司表示存款自去年底以来已有所攀升，且流动性仍然“充裕”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/nycb-stock-turns-positive-after-bank-says-deposits-have-climbed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 12:54:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国商业银行首席财务官 Carl Cederschiold FULL INTV</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-07/handelsbanken-cfo-on-earnings-executive-revamp-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典最大的房地产贷款机构瑞典商业银行 (Handelsbanken) 宣布，作为该银行执行团队变动的一部分，将取消瑞典国家总经理的职位。此次重组是在财报发布之前宣布的，该公司宣布了高于预期的股息。首席财务官 Carl Cederschiöld 加入了彭博社的 Francine Lacqua 的《脉搏》节目。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-07/handelsbanken-cfo-on-earnings-executive-revamp-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 12:26:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着 Milei 改革回到原点，阿根廷债券暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/argentina-bonds-dip-as-milei-s-reforms-sent-back-to-square-one</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷执政联盟在意识到没有足够的票数推动总统哈维尔·米莱的改革方案在众议院获得通过后，将其重新提交国会审议，导致阿根廷债券在早盘交易中下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/argentina-bonds-dip-as-milei-s-reforms-sent-back-to-square-one</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 11:57:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿里巴巴同意再次进行 250 亿美元的售后回购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/alibaba-approves-another-25-billion-of-buybacks-as-sales-miss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿里巴巴集团控股有限公司(Alibaba Group Holding Ltd.)再次批准了250亿美元的股票回购计划，吸引了担心这家中国电子商务先驱公司的增长陷入停滞的投资者，该公司正在努力抵御拼多多(PDD Holdings Inc.)等新竞争对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/alibaba-approves-another-25-billion-of-buybacks-as-sales-miss</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 11:47:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于成本打击保险部门，CVS 下调 2024 年预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/cvs-cuts-2024-forecast-as-higher-costs-hit-health-insurance-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[CVS Health Corp. 大幅削减了 2024 年运营利润和现金流指引，因为医疗费用上涨预计将损害其健康保险部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/cvs-cuts-2024-forecast-as-higher-costs-hit-health-insurance-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 11:31:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>凯雷调整薪酬计划，计划回购高达 14 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/carlyle-revamps-dealmaker-pay-plans-up-to-1-4-billion-buyback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯雷集团 (Carlyle Group Inc.) 正在彻底改革其向交易撮合者付款的方式，以便为股东释放更稳定的现金流，并批准了一项回购高达 14 亿美元股票的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/carlyle-revamps-dealmaker-pay-plans-up-to-1-4-billion-buyback</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 11:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>夜视系统公司 Theon 在首次交易中表现不佳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/night-vision-maker-theon-edges-higher-in-amsterdam-trading-debut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[夜视和热成像系统制造商 Theon International Plc 在阿姆斯特丹首次上市时股价下跌，这是近两年来荷兰城市首次上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/night-vision-maker-theon-edges-higher-in-amsterdam-trading-debut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 08:23:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银 (UBS) 提供 10 亿美元 AT1 快速启动融资计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/ubs-offers-1-billion-at1s-in-fast-start-to-year-s-funding-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团 (UBS Group AG) 在制定未来几年增发数十亿美元风险证券的计划后一天，就发行了以美元计价的额外一级票据。]]></description>
